<script type="text/javascript">
  
    function myMouseover(RowName, InvnetoryID, currentRowID) {
        var DivName = RowName + '_' + InvnetoryID;
        var myDiv = document.getElementById(DivName);

        var row = document.getElementById(currentRowID);
        var x = findPosX(row);
        var y = findPosY(row);
        var height = row.offsetHeight;
        var width = row.offsetWidth;
        var left = findPosX(row) - 15;
        var bottom = findPosY(row) + row.offsetHeight;

        myDiv.style.left = left + 'px';
        myDiv.style.top = bottom + 'px';
        myDiv.style.display = "block";
    }

    function myMouseout(RowName, InvnetoryID, RowNumber) {
        var DivName = RowName + '_' + InvnetoryID;
        var myDiv = document.getElementById(DivName);

        myDiv.style.display = "none";
    }

    //get the x postion of an html object
    function findPosX(obj) {
        var curleft = 0;
        if (obj.offsetParent)
            while (1) {
            curleft += obj.offsetLeft;
            if (!obj.offsetParent)
                break;
            obj = obj.offsetParent;
        }
        else if (obj.x)
            curleft += obj.x;
        return curleft;
    }

    //get the y postion of an html object
    function findPosY(obj) {
        var curtop = 0;
        if (obj.offsetParent)
            while (1) {
            curtop += obj.offsetTop;
            if (!obj.offsetParent)
                break;
            obj = obj.offsetParent;
        }
        else if (obj.y)
            curtop += obj.y;
        return curtop;
    }
</script>
